query:
INSERT INTO photo_collaborators (photoId, collaboratorId, createdAt)
SELECT id, collaboratorId, NOW()
FROM photos
WHERE collaboratorId IS NOT NULL
AND NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM photo_collaborators pc
  WHERE pc.photoId = photos.id AND pc.collaboratorId = photos.collaboratorId
);
